data.description: Welcome home! Whether you are looking for your permanent residence or an investment property this is perfect. 2 bedrooms with 2 full bathrooms this is all you will need. Located centrally in Raleigh ITB you're near Midtown restaurants, shopping such as Trader Joe's and Wegmans and entertainment. This one will go fast so book your showing and don't miss out!
